name: Inner Child Connection
description: This piece is inspired by the inner child, a mental entity that in psychology is related to our first memories and experiences in early stages of life. We were vulnerable when we were children and sometimes we still carry wounds. This piece is inspired by how I healed some of my inner patterns by communicating to my inner child in psilocybin. 30% of gains will be donated to "conservamos por naturaleza" to reforest Peruvian rainforest.
